casebody.data:
Byrd, Appellant, v. Alexander, Warden, Appellee.

[Cite as Byrd v. Alexander (1991), 60 Ohio St. 3d 124.]

(No. 90-1502 — Submitted April 24, 1991 — Decided June 5, 1991.) Randall M. Dana, Ohio public defender, Kenneth R. Spiert and Thomas R. Wetterer, Jr., for appellant. Lee I. Fisher, attorney general, and Donald G. Keyser, for appellee.

The certification of conflict is dismissed as moot.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
